nt_site/assets/slider__03.png\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/slider__03@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                  </picture>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"slider__slide js-slider-panel\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(max-width:1024px)\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/slider__04_sp.png 1x, /special_recruitment_site/assets/slider__04_sp@2x.png 2x\">\n                    <img class=\"kv__slider__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/slider__04.png\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/slider__04@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                  </picture>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"movie fixed-bg__container\">\n          <picture>\n            <source srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg.webp, /special_recruitment_site/assets/bg@2x.webp 2x\" type=\"image/webp\">\n            <img class=\"fixed-bg\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n          </picture>\n          <div class=\"content content--left\">\n            <div class=\"content__inner movie__inner\">\n              <div class=\"movie__spacer\">\n                <hgroup id=\"movie\" class=\"movie__heading\">\n                  <h2 class=\"slash section-heading\">\n                    <span class=\"slash__clip\">\n                      <span class=\"slash__content\"> movie </span>\n                    </span>\n                  </h2>\n                  <p class=\"movie__heading__text shuffle\">時代は自ら動かない</p>\n                  <p class=\"movie__heading__text shuffle\">\n                    意志ある人が動かしていく。\n                  </p>\n                </hgroup>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"movie-dialog__open js-analytics__thumbnail js-movie-thumbnail\" data-modal-open=\"movie-dialog\">\n                  <img class=\"movie__thumbnail\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/open_modal.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/open_modal@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"動画コンテンツを視聴する\" width=\"880\" height=\"495\" decoding=\"async\">\n                </button>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"movie__caption\">\n                Recruitment Movie<br class=\"sp-only\"><span class=\"zen-white-space\">　</span>意志ある人が動かしていく篇【60秒】\n              </p>\n              <dialog aria-label=\"TIS株式会社 新卒採用2027 スペシャルムービー\" id=\"movie-dialog\" class=\"movie-dialog\">\n                <div class=\"movie-dialog__inner\">\n                  <button type=\"button\" class=\"movie-dialog__close\" aria-label=\"動画コンテンツを終了する\">\n                    <span class=\"movie-dialog__close__line\"></span>\n                    <span class=\"movie-dialog__close__line\"></span>\n                  </button>\n                  <video class=\"movie-dialog__movie\" controls=\"\" playsinline=\"\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/TIS_recruit2023.mp4\" preload=\"auto\"></video>\n                </div>\n              </dialog>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"message fixed-bg__container\">\n          <img class=\"fixed-bg\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg@2x2.jpg 2x\">\n          <div class=\"content content--right\">\n            <div class=\"content__inner message__inner\">\n              <hgroup class=\"message__heading\" id=\"message\">\n                <h2 class=\"slash section-heading\">\n                  <span class=\"slash__clip\">\n                    <span class=\"slash__content\"> message </span>\n                  </span>\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"message__heading__text\">ムービーコンセプト</p>\n              </hgroup>\n              <picture>\n                <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/visual_sp.jpg, /special_recruitment_site/assets/visual_sp@2x.jpg 2x\">\n                <img class=\"message__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/visual.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/visual@2x.jpg 2x\" width=\"880\" height=\"438\">\n              </picture>\n              <p class=\"message__text\">\n                スマートフォン1つで、<br class=\"sp-only\">あらゆる生活シーンを<br class=\"sp-only\">カバーできるようになった。<br>\n                自動運転やロボットと共存する生活も、<br class=\"sp-only\">夢から現実のものになりつつある。 <br>\n                デジタル技術は世の中を<br class=\"sp-only\">新たな時代へと動かす、原動力に。\n              </p>\n              <p class=\"message__text\">\n                けれど何より重要なのは、<br class=\"sp-only\">技術の前にある人の意志。 <br>\n                世の中をこう変えたい、<br class=\"sp-only\">こう動かしたい、<br class=\"sp-only\">という人間にしか持ち得ない想いです。<br>\n                自分の意志で、<br class=\"sp-only\">世の中を動かすことができる場所で働きませんか。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"about fixed-bg__container\">\n          <img class=\"fixed-bg\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg@2x3.jpg 2x\">\n          <div class=\"content content--left\">\n            <div class=\"content__inner about__inner\">\n              <hgroup class=\"about__heading\" id=\"about\">\n                <h2 class=\"slash section-heading\">\n                  <span class=\"slash__clip\">\n                    <span class=\"slash__content\"> about </span>\n                  </span>\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"about__heading__text\">TISの特長</p>\n              </hgroup>\n              <img src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/about_image.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/about_image@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" class=\"about__image\">\n              <p class=\"about__intro\">\n                TISは国内大手の総合ITサービス企業として、幅広い産業をITの力で支えてきた豊富な実績と技術力を基盤とし、お客様のビジネスに貢献しています。\n              </p>\n              <section class=\"about__point\" data-fadein=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"about__point__heading\" data-yaku=\"\">\n                  「成長戦略を支えるためのIT」\n                </h3>\n                <img class=\"about__point__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-01@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                <p class=\"about__point__text\">\n                  TISは、金融、製造、流通、サービス、公共、通信など多種多様な業種にわたる3,000社以上のお客様のビジネスパートナーとして、お客様のあらゆる経営課題に真摯に向き合い続けています。<br>\n                  なかでも、金融・決済分野がTISの強みの一つです。\n                </p>\n              </section>\n              <section class=\"about__point\" data-fadein=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"about__point__heading\">\n                  50年の実績から成る、<br class=\"sp-only\">実現力と先進性。\n                </h3>\n                <img class=\"about__point__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-02@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                <p class=\"about__point__text\">\n                  TISには、高度な金融業界向けシステムの開発などを通じて培った豊富な業務ノウハウや技術力があります。アイデアを実現する力と業界をリードする先進性を活かし、今では、TIS独自のサービスも多く生み出しています。お客様のビジネスパートナーとしてニーズを見つけ、期待を超える高い品質を実現していくことが私たちの仕事です。\n                </p>\n              </section>\n              <section class=\"about__point\" data-fadein=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"about__point__heading\">\n                  提案力と課題解決力を<br class=\"sp-only\">支えるサービスメニュー。\n                </h3>\n                <img class=\"about__point__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-03@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                <p class=\"about__point__text\">\n                  TISは、サービスの自社開発に積極的に取り組み、現在200以上のサービスを提供しています。コンサルティングから運用保守、またシステム基盤の提供・構築から事務処理といったあらゆる業務領域まで。<br>\n                  これまでにない新たな課題を解決するために、新しい技術を活かしたサービス開発を進めています。\n                </p>\n              </section>\n              <section class=\"about__point\" data-fadein=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"about__point__heading\">\n                  “攻める”“やり切る”<br class=\"sp-only\">現場力、人材力。\n                </h3>\n                <img class=\"about__point__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/point-04@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                <p class=\"about__point__text\">\n                  お客様それぞれの課題に向き合い解決してきた私たちには、“攻める姿勢”“やり切る力”がDNAに刻まれており、社員が活き活きとチャレンジする文化が根づいています。多様な人材が、個々の能力を高めることでTIS全体の企業価値を向上し、社会へ貢献しています。\n                </p>\n              </section>\n              <section class=\"about__domain\">\n                <h3 class=\"about__domain__heading\">TISの事業領域</h3>\n                <figure class=\"about__domain__figure\">\n                  <figcaption class=\"about__domain__caption\">\n                    ビジネスを支える基幹システムから、高い競争力を生むアプリケーション、さらにはシステムの基盤となるプラットフォームまで。お客様の経営課題を把握し、潜在的なニーズを先取りしたITサービスを幅広くお届けしています。\n                  </figcaption>\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/domain_image_sp.jpg, /special_recruitment_site/assets/domain_image_sp@2x.jpg 2x\">\n                    <img class=\"about__domain__image\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/domain_image.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/domain_image@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n                  </picture>\n                </figure>\n              </section>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"workspace\">\n          <hgroup id=\"workspace\" class=\"workspace__heading\">\n            <h2 class=\"slash section-heading workspace__heading__main\">\n              <span class=\"slash__clip\">\n                <span class=\"slash__content\"> workspace </span>\n              </span>\n            </h2>\n            <p class=\"workspace__heading__text\">\n              良質なアイデアを生み出す多彩なオフィス空間。\n            </p>\n          </hgroup>\n          <div class=\"workspace__gallery\">\n            <div class=\"workspace__gallery__line\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-01@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-02.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-02@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-03.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-03@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-04@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-05@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-06.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-06@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-07.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-07@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-08.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-08@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-01@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-02.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-02@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-03.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-03@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-04@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-05@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-06.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-06@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-07.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-07@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-08.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/a-08@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"workspace__gallery__line\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-01@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-02.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-02@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-03.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-03@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-04@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-05@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-06.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-06@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-07.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-07@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-08.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-08@2x.jpg 2x\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-01@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-02.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-02@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-03.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-03@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-04@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-05@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-06.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-06@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-07.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-07@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <img class=\"workspace__gallery__panel\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-08.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/b-08@2x.jpg 2x\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"recruit fixed-bg__container\">\n          <img class=\"fixed-bg\" src=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg4.jpg\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/bg@2x4.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n          <div class=\"content content--left\">\n            <div class=\"content__inner recruit__inner\">\n              <hgroup class=\"recruit__heading\" id=\"cta\">\n                <h2 class=\"slash section-heading recruit__heading__main\">\n                  <span class=\"slash__clip\">\n                    <span class=\"slash__content\"> recruit </span>\n                  </span>\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"recruit__heading__text\">\n                  時代を動かす一歩を、ここから。\n                </p>\n              </hgroup>\n              <div class=\"recruit__link\">\n                <div>\n                  <h3 class=\"recruit__link__heading\">\n                    さらに詳しい採用情報はこちらから\n                  </h3>\n                  <div class=\"recruit__link__block\">\n                    <a class=\"recruit__link__button recruit__link__button--black\" href=\"https://www.tis.co.jp/recruit/\">\n                      新卒採用情報サイト\n                    </a>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <h3 class=\"recruit__link__heading\">エントリーはこちらから</h3>\n                  <div class=\"recruit__link__block\">\n                    <!-- Begin mynavi Navi Link -->\n                    <a class=\"recruit__link__button recruit__link__button--white recruit__link__button--mynavi\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp1143/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n                      <img class=\"recruit__link__logo recruit__link__logo--mainabi\" src=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/conts/kigyo/2027/logo/banner_logo_195_60.gif\" alt=\"マイナビ2027\" border=\"0\" width=\"195\" height=\"60\" decoding=\"auto\">\n                    </a>\n                    <!-- End mynavi Navi Link -->\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"recruit__x\">\n                <h3 class=\"recruit__x__heading\">\n                  TIS【新卒採用】アカウント<br>\n                  （旧Twitter）\n                </h3>\n                <a class=\"recruit__x__button\" href=\"https://x.com/tis_recruit\" target=\"_blank\">\n                  <img class=\"recruit__link__logo recruit__link__logo--x\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%20width='63'%20height='63'%20viewBox='0%200%2063%2063'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cclipPath%20id='clip-path'%3e%3crect%20id='長方形_17360'%20data-name='長方形%2017360'%20width='47.754'%20height='45'%20transform='translate(231.676%201970.5)'%20fill='none'%20stroke='%23fff'%20stroke-width='0.1'/%3e%3c/clipPath%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cg%20id='グループ_100737'%20data-name='グループ%20100737'%20transform='translate(-557%20-8263)'%3e%3cg%20id='グループ_100736'%20data-name='グループ%20100736'%20transform='translate(249%2030)'%3e%3cpath%20id='パス_398779'%20data-name='パス%20398779'%20d='M31.5,0A31.5,31.5,0,1,1,0,31.5,31.5,31.5,0,0,1,31.5,0Z'%20transform='translate(308%208233)'%20fill='%23000'/%3e%3cg%20id='X_icon_white'%20transform='translate(316%208242)'%3e%3cg%20id='X_icon_white-2'%20data-name='X_icon_white'%20transform='translate(-231.676%20-1970.5)'%20clip-path='url(%23clip-path)'%3e%3cpath%20id='logo'%20d='M17.492,12.719,28.434,0H25.841l-9.5,11.044L8.752,0H0L11.475,16.7,0,30.038H2.593L12.626,18.375,20.64,30.038h8.752l-11.9-17.319Zm-3.552,4.128-1.163-1.663L3.527,1.952H7.51l7.466,10.679,1.163,1.663,9.7,13.881H21.86L13.941,16.848Z'%20transform='translate(240.855%201977.936)'%20fill='%23fff'/%3e%3c/g%3e%3c/g%3e%3c/g%3e%3c/g%3e%3c/svg%3e\" alt=\"X（旧Twitter）のプロフィールを見る\" width=\"37\" height=\"38\">\n                </a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <footer class=\"site-footer\">\n          <nav class=\"site-footer__nav\">\n            <ul class=\"site-footer__nav__list\">\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"https://www.tis.co.jp/termsofuse/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                  サイトのご利用について\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"https://www.tis.co.jp/tis_securitypolicy/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                  情報セキュリティ方針\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"https://www.tis.co.jp/cookie_policy/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                  クッキー（Cookie）ポリシー\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </nav>\n          <div class=\"site-footer__corp\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.tis.co.jp/\">\n              <img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" srcset=\"/special_recruitment_site/assets/footer_logo@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"TIS株式会社\" width=\"83\" height=\"14\">\n            </a>\n            <p class=\"site-footer__rights\">\n              ©2025&nbsp;TIS&nbsp;Inc.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </footer>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n  \n\n</body></html>","finalUrl":"https://www.tis.co.jp/special_recruitment_site/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T19:02:32.138Z"}